urdu transliteration text:
Ali ki Beti pay guzreen Qayamateyn Kitni, Dayaar e Ghair Mei Jhayleen Musibateyn Kitni,Tabhi to Shaam Mei Roey Lahu Imam, Khuda Khair Karay
Therefore in Shaam, cried out the blood of Imam,
@HujjatELC

hashr se pehle imam e zama jo aayengeAli ki tegh bhi 'akhtar' wo saath laayengeYazeediyo se woh lenge jo inteqam khuda khair kare
Before the end, when Imam Zamana reappears,
@HujjatELC

bazar e shaam me zainab jo berida hai khadi,bimaare sayyede abid pe kya kathan hai ghadi,bhare bazaar me harsu hai majma e aam khuda khair.
Make Allah make all well
@HujjatELC

janabe ghazi ka sar naize pe tadapta tha,bimar qaidi ki ankho se khun barasta tha,laeen leta tha zainab ka jab bhi naam khuda khair.
Imam Sajjad shed tears of blood, when the oppressor takes the name Zainab,
@HujjatELC
